branchCategory.description:
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;With its internally piloted operation, the AR*23/35
regulator provides excellent pressure control in higher flow ranges.&#xa0; Connection sizes from &#xbc;” to 2” are available.&#xa0; Set pressure ranges of 3 to 30 psi (0.02 to
0.2 MPa) and 7 to 120 psi (0.05 to 0.83 MPa) optimize user adjustability.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

